              <h3 class="title">
               <a href="/news/2nd-armed-standoff-in-2-weeks-ends-tragically-in-fond-du-lac-county">
                2nd armed standoff in 2 weeks ends 'tragically' in Fond du Lac County
               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>
             <p class="dek">
              A second armed standoff in as many weeks in Fond du Lac County "ended tragically" early Sunday, March 21.
             </p>

            <div class="info">
             <header class="info-header">
              <h3 class="title">
               <a href="/news/hand-sanitizer-recalled-because-containers-resemble-water-bottles">
                Hand sanitizer recalled because containers resemble water bottles
               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>
             <p class="dek">
              A brand of hand sanitizers from a North Carolina-based manufacturer is being recalled out of fear that the containers may resemble water bottles, according to the U.S. Food and Drug Administration.
             </p>

             <a href="/podcasts/open-record-relief-package-passed">

            <div class="info">
             <header class="info-header">
              <h3 class="title">
               <a href="/sports/no-1-seed-baylor-beats-wisconsin-76-63-to-reach-sweet-16">
                No. 1 seed Baylor beats Wisconsin 76-63 to reach Sweet 16
               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>
             <p class="dek">
              Davion Mitchell scored 16 points and spearheaded a dominant defensive first half, helping top-seeded Baylor avoid another NCAA Tournament upset with a 76-63 win over Wisconsin on Sunday.
             </p>

            <div class="info">
             <header class="info-header">
              <h3 class="title">
               <a href="/news/gop-us-rep-tom-reed-to-retire-after-sexual-misconduct-accusation">
                GOP US Rep. Tom Reed to retire after sexual misconduct accusation
               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>
             <p class="dek">
              U.S. Rep. Tom Reed, a Republican from western New York who was accused last week of rubbing a female lobbyist’s back and unhooking her bra without her consent in 2017, apologized to the woman on Sunday and announced that he will not run for reelection next year.
             </p>

            <div class="info">
             <header class="info-header">
              <h3 class="title">
               <a href="/news/gop-us-rep-tom-reed-to-retire-after-sexual-misconduct-accusation">
                GOP US Rep. Tom Reed to retire after sexual misconduct accusation
               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>
             <p class="dek">
              U.S. Rep. Tom Reed, a Republican from western New York who was accused last week of rubbing a female lobbyist’s back and unhooking her bra without her consent in 2017, apologized to the woman on Sunday and announced that he will not run for reelection next year.
             </p>
             <!-- -->
             <!-- -->

                     <img alt="Lava spews as Iceland volcano comes to life for first time in 6,000 years" data-v-0cd7fcba="" src="https://images.foxtv.com/static.fox6now.com/www.fox6now.com/content/uploads/2021/03/592/333/storyful-iceland-volcano-lava.jpg?ve=1&amp;tl=1"/>

            <div class="info">
             <header class="info-header">
              <h3 class="title">
               <a href="/news/lava-spews-as-iceland-volcano-comes-to-life-for-first-time-in-6000-years">
                Lava spews as Iceland volcano comes to life for first time in 6,000 years
               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>
             <p class="dek">
              The Fagradals Mountain volcano had been dormant for 6,000 years, and this is the first volcanic eruption in this area of the country in nearly 800 years.
             </p>
